title: Google Chrome
summary: Google Chrome is a free Web browser developed by Google. It's based on the Chromium open source project. Some key differences are described on BrowserStack. Chrome supports its own layout called Blink. Note that the iOS version of Chrome uses that platform's WebView, not Blink.
